deal_name: Nordbyte Logistics — AI SDR Risk Pilot

transcript.speaker: Maya
transcript.text: Hi Alex, thanks for jumping on again. We thought it might be useful to quickly align after you had a chance to review the materials.

transcript.speaker: Alex
transcript.text: Yeah, no problem. We’ve gone through most of it internally.

transcript.speaker: Sam
transcript.text: Great. Were there any major concerns or open questions we can help clarify?

transcript.speaker: Alex
transcript.text: Nothing blocking per se. It’s more about prioritization right now.

transcript.speaker: Maya
transcript.text: Understood. Is that mainly on the budget side or security?

transcript.speaker: Alex
transcript.text: A bit of both. Security always takes longer than expected, and finance wants to see how this compares to other initiatives.

transcript.speaker: Sam
transcript.text: Makes sense. From our side, we’re happy to keep this lightweight and flexible.

transcript.speaker: Alex
transcript.text: Yeah, that helps. I just can’t commit to a concrete timeline yet.

transcript.speaker: Maya
transcript.text: Would it make sense to check back in, say, in a couple of weeks?

transcript.speaker: Sam
transcript.text: In the meantime, is there anything else you’d need from us?

transcript.speaker: Alex
transcript.text: Not at the moment. If something comes up, I’ll reach out.

transcript.speaker: Maya
transcript.text: Sounds good. Thanks again for the time.
